dn_search_result' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[10]</a>。法人看好聯電下半年營運表現將優於上半年，預期將調漲晶圓代工價格，目標價紛紛上調，最高上看120元  <a href='https://money.udn.com/money/story/5739/9498773?from=edn_search_result' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a> <a href='https://money.udn.com/money/story/5710/9497875?from=edn_search_result' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[3]</a> <a href='https://money.udn.com/money/story/5739/9495916?from=edn_search_result' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[11]</a> <a href='https://money.udn.com/money/story/5607/9454763?from=edn_search_result' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[12]</a> <a href='https://money.udn.com/money/story/5739/9453335?from=edn_search_result' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[13]</a> <a href='https://money.udn.com/money/story/5612/9449028?from=edn_search_result' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[14]</a>。此外，公司董事會也決議實施庫藏股，預計買回上限5萬張，以強化股東權益  <a href='https://money.udn.com/money/story/5739/9498773?from=edn_search_result' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a> <a href='https://money.udn.com/money/story/5612/9472870?from=edn_search_result' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[7]</a>。"
